title: Godzilla
overview: A mysterious creature causes a meltdown at a nuclear power plant. Years later, the monster goes on a rampage that can only be stopped by Godzilla.

title: Godzilla
overview: When a giant monster created by nuclear tests descends upon New York, it's up to the U.S. Army and an odd team of investigators to stop the creature.

title: Godzilla
overview: In this original version of the kaiju classic, nuclear testing produces a seemingly unstoppable beast that rampages through the streets of Tokyo.

title: Shin Godzilla
overview: Japan is plunged into chaos when a skyscraper-sized lizard monster rises from the deep of Tokyo Bay and lays waste to Tokyo.

title: Godzilla: Planet of the Monsters
overview: A desperate group of refugees attempts to recolonize Earth 20,000 years after Godzilla took over. But one young man wants revenge above all else.

title: Godzilla, King of the Monsters!
overview: A 400-foot dinosaur-like beast, awoken from undersea hibernation off the Japanese coast by atomic-bomb testing, attacks Tokyo.

title: Godzilla vs. Biollante
overview: Uncontrolled scientific research creates a hybrid that's part plant, part Godzilla and all evil! Only the real Godzilla can stop it.

title: The Return of Godzilla
overview: The Japanese government suppresses news of Godzilla's return as political tensions increase between the US and USSR, both of whom are willing to bomb Japan to stop the monster.

title: Godzilla, the Monster of the Pacific Ocean
originalTitle: Godzilla, le Monstre de L'Océan Pacifique

title: Godzilla vs. Kong
overview: Legends collide as these mythic adversaries meet in a spectacular battle for the ages, with the world's fate hanging in the balance.

title: Godzilla: King of the Monsters
overview: When ancient god-sized monsters rise again, the crypto-zoological agency Monarch faces off against Godzilla, Mothra, Rodan, and King Ghidorah as they all vie for supremacy.

title: Godzilla Minus One
overview: In postwar Japan, a new terror rises; Godzilla. Will the devastated people be able to survive... let alone fight back?

title: Godzilla Raids Again
overview: Godzilla battles an irradiated Ankylosaur and destroys Osaka in the process.

title: Godzilla vs. Mechagodzilla II
overview: Godzilla is back! But he must battle Mechagodzilla II, a giant metal robot that is Japan's greatest hope for ending Godzilla's reign of terror.

title: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire
overview: The ultimate Titan team-up! This explosive action-adventure follows Godzilla and the almighty Kong as they face the most dangerous threat from Hollow World yet ... one that challenges their very existence and the survival of the human race.
originalTitle: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire

title: Godzilla vs. Gigan
overview: Suspicious of his employer, a manga artist assembles a team to investigate a garbled tape message while two kaijus launch their own plan of action.
originalTitle: 地球攻撃命令 ゴジラ対ガイガン

title: Godzilla: Tokyo S.O.S.
overview: One year after the fight between Godzilla and Mechagodzilla, the two monsters along with Mothra face off in a conclusive battle royale.
originalTitle: ゴジラ×モスラ×メカゴジラ／東京SOS

title: Godzilla 2000: Millennium
overview: Godzilla enters the 21st century with a battle against alien invaders who use the creature’s DNA to create an indestructible monster.
originalTitle: ゴジラ2000 ミレニアム
